nk\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/07/15/economy/china-gdp-growth/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong(CNN Business) China's economic growth slumped to its lowest level in nearly three decades as the world's second largest economy feels the effects of a prolonged trade war with the United States.<br />\n<br />\nThe country's gross domestic product grew at 6.2% in the quarter ended June, the slowest quarterly growth rate since 1992 and down from 6.4% in the previous quarter, according to government figures released on Monday.<br />\n<br />\nAnd the Chinese economy will continue to face &quot;downward pressure&quot; in the second half of this year, the country's National Bureau of Statistics said in a statement."},{"pid":"05a5d9666136a04036bf431482df75870b17634b","tid":1302524,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"435a7584c124cee8e890f88b73d0a633b837e53c","tid":1302524,"uid":33263,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T07:28:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2019/07/15/economy/china-gdp-growth/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2Feconomy%2Fchina-gdp-growth%2Findex.html&d=QYAfZ%2BMwCyPDsUhWB4j8CgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e6a86531\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2019%2F07%2F15%2Feconomy%2Fchina-gdp-growth%2Findex.html&h=691b4b4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2019/07/15/economy/china-gdp-growth/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong(CNN Business) China's economic growth slumped to its lowest level in nearly three decades as the world's second largest economy feels the effects of a prolonged trade war with the United States.<br />\n<br />\nThe country's gross domestic product grew at 6.2% in the quarter ended June, the slowest quarterly growth rate since 1992 and down from 6.4% in the previous quarter, according to government figures released on Monday.<br />\n<br />\nAnd the Chinese economy will continue to face &quot;downward pressure&quot; in the second half of this year, the country's National Bureau of Statistics said in a statement."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T22:57:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddc166a9c272577069490bb0162d1124fcf6b55","tid":1302524,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"820b909fda2fdc96cd81d7d98846a8fde71dd371","tid":1302524,"uid":145247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37f1609ff8e7bf23087b929f144cdccd8e57dcb1","tid":1302524,"uid":89349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}